#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 5. Aññatitthiyapeyyālavagga → virāgasuttaṃ (bj) | virāga (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Aññatitthiyapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "5. Abbreviated Texts on Followers of Other Paths"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 41. Rāgavirāgasutta → aññatitthiyavaggo (s1-3) | aññatitthiyapeyyālo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Rāgavirāgasutta"
msgstr "41. The Fading Away of Greed"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.2"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you:"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘kimatthiyaṃ, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti, evaṃ puṭṭhā "
"tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha:"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverends, what’s the purpose of living the spiritual life with the ascetic "
"Gotama?’ You should answer them like this:"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.4"
msgid "‘rāgavirāgatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is the fading "
"away of greed.’"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.5"
msgid "Sace pana vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "If wanderers who follow other paths were to ask you:"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.6"
msgid ""
"‘atthi panāvuso, maggo, atthi paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyā’ti, evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, "
"bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha:"
msgstr ""
"‘Is there a path and a practice for the fading away of greed?’ You should "
"answer them like this:"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.7"
msgid "‘atthi kho, āvuso, maggo, atthi paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyā’ti."
msgstr "‘There is a path and a practice for the fading away of greed.’"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.8"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, maggo, katamā ca paṭipadā rāgavirāgāya?"
msgstr ""
"And what is that path, what is that practice for the fading away of greed?"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.9"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.10"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, maggo, ayaṃ paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyāti."
msgstr "This is the path, this is the practice for the fading away of greed."

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.12"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ "
"byākareyyāthā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When questioned by wanderers who follow other paths, that’s how you should "
"answer them.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.13"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
